scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 4 to 157 comprise the entire Schedule to the 2002 ISDA Master Agreement, including all its Parts (1-5) and the bespoke elections, representations, and amendments between the parties. The text before line 4 is cover/identification, and after line 157 is execution/signature. There is no evidence of CSA annexes or standard pre-print Master Agreement text within this span.
